metadata.name: story of Ye Mingsheng,
metadata.description:
change, to Ye Mingsheng finish, he hesitated, and then very confused inquiry; "Young Master, can you tell me why you did this? These are old people who have been with you for years..."



Faced with Ye Tie's question, Ye Mingsheng gave a wry smile, shook his head and said, "I don't want to do this either, but there is no way. If we don't do this, we will die."



Although still do not understand the reason why Ye Mingsheng did so, but see their young master said so serious, Ye iron face is also become serious, heavy nodded and said: "young master, I will get things done."
